library(ggplot2)
DSM_HARV_df <- as.data.frame(DSM_HARV, xy=TRUE)
ggplot() +
  geom_raster(data=DSM_HARV_df, aes(x=x,y=y, fill=HARV_dsmCrop)) +
  #scale_fill_viridis_c() +
  coord_quickmap()
